 />\n\t2) fierce pose<br />\n\t3) fierce weather<br />\n\t4) fierce expression<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tAt that time, money was a little tight. Competition in the club business was fierce. There were many overhead costs just to keep the place running and stay relevant in the circle. Other than the basic cost of maintaining the staff and facility, there were also the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/variable\" target=\"_blank\">variable</a> costs of food and drinks. The up-keeping of the premise also accounted for a large section of the budget as interior decor had to be updated constantly to keep the club interesting as well as to be able to hold various functions.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/167944471455/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p799318/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p799318\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p799259/\">这奥运村会不会住坏我们国宝级的运动员？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p799643/\">林心如霍建华大婚还珠三美合体 老外都说美</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p798526/\">王毅怒斥加拿大记者这视频 看一遍赞一遍</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p798943/\">爱宠大机密！今年夏天最好看的动画片来啦！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p799681/\">河里飘尸体走路上被抢 里约奥运会这槽点啊</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p799986/\">首个轮椅男模：不轻言放弃 他帅成了一道闪电</a></li><li s